title: CleanMyMac v2.0.5.dmg
description:
Installation Instructions: 
------------------
- Open "CleanMyMac v2.0.5.dmg"
- Drag/Copy "CleanMyMac 2.app" to your "Applications" folder.
- Thats it, you now have a fully functional copy of CleanMyMac 2.


Important Note: 
------------------
- You should block CleanMyMac 2 with Little Snitch. This step is not necessary but it is recommended. Tutorial:
- Don't update CleanMyMac 2 as updating it might cause a problem. You have been warned.
- After opening the app if it complains that it is damaged then run the following command from terminal (make sure that you change /path/to/application.app to the relative application path). Command:  xattr -d -r com.apple.quarantine path/to/application.app
